---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Blicksel Picks - Your Trusted Product Review Source"
  description="Learn about Blicksel Picks, our mission to provide honest Amazon product reviews, and meet our team of expert reviewers."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-white shadow-sm">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            About Blicksel Picks
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Your trusted source for honest, comprehensive Amazon product reviews and buying guides.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              At Blicksel Picks, we believe that making informed purchasing decisions shouldn't be overwhelming. 
              With thousands of products available on Amazon, finding the right one can be challenging. 
              That's where we come in.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Our mission is simple: to provide honest, detailed, and unbiased reviews of Amazon products 
              across various categories. We test products thoroughly, research extensively, and present our 
              findings in an easy-to-understand format that helps you make confident purchasing decisions.
            </p>
            
            <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Real Testing:</strong> We actually purchase and test the products we review, not just rely on manufacturer specifications.</li>
              <li><strong>Unbiased Reviews:</strong> Our reviews are honest and transparent, highlighting both pros and cons of each product.</li>
              <li><strong>Comprehensive Analysis:</strong> We consider factors like value for money, build quality, user experience, and long-term durability.</li>
              <li><strong>Regular Updates:</strong> We update our reviews when products change or when better alternatives become available.</li>
              <li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> We listen to our readers' feedback and review requests to ensure we're covering products you care about.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
            <p>
              Every product we review goes through a rigorous evaluation process:
            </p>
            
            <ol>
              <li><strong>Research:</strong> We research the product category, compare specifications, and identify key features to evaluate.</li>
              <li><strong>Purchase & Testing:</strong> We buy the product at full price and test it in real-world conditions for several weeks.</li>
              <li><strong>Comparison:</strong> We compare the product against similar options in the same category and price range.</li>
              <li><strong>Analysis:</strong> We analyze performance, build quality, value proposition, and user experience.</li>
              <li><strong>Review Writing:</strong> We write comprehensive reviews that highlight strengths, weaknesses, and our overall recommendation.</li>
            </ol>
            
            <h2>Categories We Cover</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Electronics</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Home & Garden</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 100 4m0-4v2m0-6V4"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Kitchen</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Health & Fitness</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zM7 3H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a4 4 0 004 4h2a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Beauty</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Sports</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="flex justify-center mb-2">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V9a1 1 0 011-1h1a2 2 0 100-4H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V5a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="font-medium">Gaming</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
            <p>
              We believe in complete transparency with our readers:
            </p>
            
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Affiliate Disclosure:</strong> We are participants in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. When you make a purchase through our affiliate links, we earn a small commission at no additional cost to you.</li>
              <li><strong>Editorial Independence:</strong> Our affiliate partnerships do not influence our review process or recommendations. We only recommend products we genuinely believe in.</li>
              <li><strong>Honest Opinions:</strong> We share our genuine opinions and experiences, even if it means recommending against expensive products.</li>
              <li><strong>Update Policy:</strong> We regularly update our reviews and buying guides to reflect changes in product availability, pricing, and new alternatives.</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
              Have a product you'd like us to review? Found an error in one of our reviews? 
              We'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700">contact page</a> 
              to get in touch.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              You can also follow us on social media for the latest updates, deal alerts, and behind-the-scenes content.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Section -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Meet Our Team</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-accent-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">JS</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">John Smith</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 mb-3">Founder & Chief Editor</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                With over 10 years of experience in product testing and consumer electronics, 
                John founded Blicksel Picks to help consumers make better purchasing decisions.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">MR</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Maria Rodriguez</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-600 mb-3">Senior Product Reviewer</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Maria specializes in home and kitchen products. Her attention to detail and 
                practical testing approach helps readers find products that truly work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>